<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bid-n">bid <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪd/    美 /bɪd/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(尤指拍卖时的) 出价；投标：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ve <strong>made a bid</strong> of nearly £400,000,000 <strong>for</strong> the company.
我们出价近四亿英镑收购那家公司。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If a city has plenty of parks, this could help its bid to be an Olympic city. 
如果一个城市拥有众多公园，这将有助于它申请成为奥运会的主办城市。</p><footer>译林④ – 2</footer></div></div>